body_html:
Hi:
I add "checkReleaseBuilds false" below to resolve the "default constructor" issue,
lintOptions {
abortOnError false
checkReleaseBuilds false
}

and finally the "libtensorflow_demo.so" can be loaded in x86 emulator.

However once launch the demo app, the error occurs ,
and I'm not sure if it's because the x86 issue or not ?!
